"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Confrontation in battle</h2>\n<h3>Between armies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:20\">JDG 20:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:11\">2CH 14:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:25\">JDG 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:1\">1SA 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:2\">1SA 17:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:1\">1SA 31:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:17\">2SA 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:3\">2CH 13:3</a></p>\n<h3>Between individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">1SA 17:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:21\">2SA 23:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:14\">1KI 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:11\">2KI 14:11</a></p>\n<h2>Personal confrontation</h2>\n<h3>Between individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11\">GAL 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:20\">EXO 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:19\">2SA 22:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:18\">PSA 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:24\">1KI 22:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:18\">2CH 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:10\">JER 28:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:26\">JHN 18:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:8\">ACT 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:2\">ACT 23:2</a></p>\n<h3>Between individuals and groups</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:3\">NUM 16:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:6\">ACT 18:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:7\">1SA 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:2\">EZK 16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:28-Acts5:29\">ACT 5:28–5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:9\">ACT 6:9</a></p>\n<h3>Between believers and a sinner</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:3\">LUK 17:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:17\">LEV 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:15\">MAT 18:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:19-Jas5:20\">JAS 5:19–5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Confrontation between Jesus Christ and the Pharisees</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:53-Luke11:54\">LUK 11:53–11:54</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:1\">MAT 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15\">MAT 22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:16\">MRK 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:5\">MRK 7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:2\">LUK 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:39\">LUK 19:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:13\">JHN 8:13</a></p>\n<h2>Confrontation with God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:32\">JOB 9:32</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:4-Acts9:5\">ACT 9:4–9:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:24\">GEN 32:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:7\">EXO 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:22\">NUM 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:21\">2CH 35:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:13\">JOB 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:14\">JOB 31:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:5\">JOB 33:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:13\">PSA 17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:11\">ISA 30:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:24\">JER 50:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:17\">ACT 11:17</a></p>",
